\mt1 Proverbs  
\c 3  
\p
\v 5 Gunwoybuk ay-negirdi nilorndo. Niyepu ngurr-menmayin Adjarriwu Bapa Aganidji. Wurru nguwurr-djarriwu ngubu-wun. Galu ngud-burro gunwoybuk ngu-negi ngad-bolondo. Ngayipurrpu galu ngubu-barrwa gunmuka.   